      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Experience an adrenaline-filled outdoor adventure at Skyline Luge Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia’s exciting gravity-powered ride attraction. Perfect for families, friends, and thrill-seekers, the luge offers a unique downhill racing experience where you control your own speed.Choose from purpose-built tracks featuring twists, turns, tunnels, and scenic views as you navigate your way down the hillside. Whether you prefer a leisurely ride or a fast-paced descent, the luge is designed for riders of all experience levels.Your adventure begins with a scenic Skyride chairlift that takes you to the starting point, offering panoramic views before the fun begins. Combining excitement, safety, and accessibility, Skyline Luge Kuala Lumpur is a must-visit attraction for visitors of all ages."
          }
        ]
      },
