        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Valid on the selected visit date only. Tickets are for individual use and must not be shared. The quantity selected indicates the number of times you can enjoy both the Luge and Skyride. Eligibility Adult Ticket: Valid for guests aged 6 years old and above. Luge: Riders must be at least 110cm tall to ride alone. Skyride: Riders above 135cm may ride alone. Hyfly Zipline: Weight restriction applies (30kg – 140kg). This activity is not recommended for guests with medical conditions (e.g., high blood pressure, epilepsy), pregnant women, or seniors. Attraction Access The quantity indicates the number of times you can enjoy both the luge and Skyride. With Skyline Luge Kuala Lumpur featuring four distinct tracks, we recommend taking 4 or 5 luge rides for a comprehensive experience. No mobile phone photography or videography is allowed while riding the Skyride or Luge for safety reasons. Safety helmets must be worn at all times while riding. Guests must follow all safety instructions and staff guidance during the activity. Operations may be suspended or modified due to weather conditions, maintenance, or safety reasons without prior notice. Additional Information Dangerous materials such as bottles, firecrackers, lasers, and other items that may disturb other guests are prohibited inside the venue. Important Notes Management reserves the right to refuse admission or participation to guests who do not comply with safety rules or height restrictions."
              }
            ]
          }
